<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Accord2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Accord,</orth> vb. to agree: <cit><quote>my consent and fair --ing voice,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.2.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 2, 19</bibl></cit>. Followed by <cit><quote>to:</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 3, 90</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 4, 139</bibl>. By <cit><quote>with:</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 269</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.2.77" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 2, 77</bibl>. By an inf.: <bibl n="shak. lc 3" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 2, 86</bibl>.
